  <section>
    <h2 id="how-we-evaluate">How we evaluate</h2>
    <p>We score each grinder on <strong>brew quality</strong>, <strong>grinder consistency</strong>, <strong>usability</strong>, <strong>cleaning burden</strong>, and <strong>value for money</strong>. Under-$200 picks get extra weight for retention/static behavior because messy grinders quickly become shelf ornaments.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 id="budget-tier-winners">Budget-tier winners</h2>
