      <li><strong>Best under $100: OXO Brew Conical Burr</strong> — easiest low-cost step up from blade grinders with dependable filter range performance.</li>
      <li><strong>Best $100-$149: Fellow Opus</strong> — strongest blend of filter clarity and entry-espresso capability in the mid-budget slot.</li>
      <li><strong>Best $150-$200: Turin SK40</strong> — best pick when you want single-dose workflow and stronger espresso control without crossing $200.</li>
